[2.396, "o", "\r\nAI: I have access to the following tools:\r\n\r\n*   `summary()`: Provides a high-level overview of active applications, process groups, and recently exited processes.\r\n*   `inspect(pid)`: Returns detailed metadata for a given process ID (PID), including command line, parent information, file and network effects.\r\n*   `search(query)`: Searches for processes matching a regex pattern in names, paths, or connection/file targets.\r\n*   `family(pid)`: Retrieves the process lineage (ancestors and descendants) for a specified PID.\r\n\r\n\r\n> "]
