[3.241, "o", "\r\nAI: I am unable to open that file. These connections and file accesses should be noted as suspicious. Between waybar and the antigravity application, there seems to be something connecting to google servers without an explanation. It would be important to examine the source code, as it is very suspicious.\r\n\r\nThe most important thing to do is ensure `exfil_sim.py` is no longer running, as it is performing unauthorized credential harvesting.\r\n\r\n\r\n> "]
